##Scalling

```
StandardScaler: If Shapiro-Wilk test yields a p-value greater than 0.05 and skewness is between -0.5 and 0.5.
MinMaxScaler: If Shapiro-Wilk test yields a p-value less than 0.05 and skewness is between -1 and -0.5 or between 0.5 and 1.
RobustScaler: If Shapiro-Wilk test yields a p-value less than 0.05 and skewness is greater than 1 or less than -1.
```

